'''罗格斯大学肯顿分校法学院'''（The School of Law at Rutgers, the State University of New Jersey--Camden<ref name="Rutgers, the State University of New Jersey--Newark " />，简称 Rutgers School of Law–Camden）是一所自1908年起在[[美国|美国]][[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[肯顿_(新泽西州)|肯顿]]创设的法学院，附属于{{link-en|罗格斯大学肯顿分校|Rutgers–Camden}}。<ref name="Rutgers, the State University of New Jersey--Newark ">{{cite web | url=http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/rutgers-the-state-university-of-new-jersey-camden-03097 | title=Rutgers, the State University of New Jersey--Camden | accessdate=2012-10-02 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130831005416/http://grad-schools.usnews.rankingsandreviews.com/best-graduate-schools/top-law-schools/rutgers-the-state-university-of-new-jersey-camden-03097 | archivedate=2013-08-31 }}</ref>
该学院在《[[美国新闻与世界报道|美国新闻与世界报道]]》的[[美国法学院排名|法学院排名]]中排名81名。<ref name="Top 2012 Law School Rankings">{{cite web | url=http://www.top-law-schools.com/rankings.html | title=Top 2012 Law School Rankings | accessdate=2012-10-02 | archive-date=2013-07-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707060344/http://www.top-law-schools.com/rankings.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

[[罗格斯大学|罗格斯大学]][[罗格斯大学纽瓦克分校|纽瓦克分校]]内也有一所[[罗格斯大学纽瓦克分校法学院|法学院]]，与该院实力相近，本来两院将一起被合并进该州另外一所不甚有名的公立大学[[罗文大学|罗文大学]]，但遭到了师生的强烈反对。<ref name="N.J. College Combination Stirs New Doubts">{{cite web | url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303561504577493230674375636.html | title=N.J. College Combination Stirs New Doubts | accessdate=2012-10-03}}</ref>
